{"tid":558062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴翻側慘劇示意圖","createTime":"2018-02-12T02:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T04:55:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75e2c738bed0748af113fd2d4b2e2775e1c570e1","tid":558062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180212/20303135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F20303135&d=wJaK6%2F6GY3%2FwCZnQHI7hgTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=93eec76c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F20303135&h=b48a74cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180212/20303135</a><br />\n<br />\n九巴翻側慘劇示意圖<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180212/large/a0602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180212%2Flarge%2Fa0602a.gif&h=c12c5186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳一張懷疑是肇事車牌LX9991九巴的黑盒數據圖，其中一段約200米的路程顯示為超速紅線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180212/large/a0602b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180212%2Flarge%2Fa0602b.gif&h=4fa35665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t逾百人路祭　有人從澳門趕來港錯過儀式子激動跪地「阿媽我嚟遲咗」<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t多一塊靈牌　留醫老伯「被死亡」<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t約好團年　岳母痛失女婿<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t顧家男慘死　遺女兒弟妹<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t家屬憑網上照認出垂危村長<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t女兒fb集氣為命危父祈禱<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t家屬趕赴現場見最後一面淒哭聲不絕　隔馬路呼喚至親<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t殮房通宵開放　家屬分批認屍<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t重型吊車扶正巴士殘骸<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t九巴代表帶果籃探傷者<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t意外12小時後解封　車站已鏟平　殘肢　財物　遍現場<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t災難遇害者辨認組助認遺體<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t村民：現場等巴士好似等死<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t市民致哀　痛罵車長應負責<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t疑似肇事巴士黑盒數據顯示超速車長遭扣押　警查是否涉誤殺<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t玻璃射臉　婦爬血路逃生<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t「巴膠」車長即刪fb賬戶<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t區議會開會研路段減速<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t工會質疑兼職培訓不足<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t救急扶危　等4小時也值得市民心連心　捐血人龍長百米<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t唐文龍：等幾耐都無所謂<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t馬會慈善機構撥逾三千萬援助<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\tTVB記者疑為直播阻救援<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t議員促年初二「頭七」停放煙花<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t九巴慘劇掟彎掟碎19家庭　痛<br />\n頭條 5小時前"},{"pid":"f640a5779a4cb322b37ebbd858364453e59f81b9","tid":558062,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f45ecbb0288ed96cc42186ca40aea4721234e5f8","tid":558062,"uid":107862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T04:49:51.000Z","msg":"向下踩，往死裡踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8003de6b8c557b78182a3f221624961824f51c05","tid":558062,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"第一日已經估到班廢老一定又人踏人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47aff79105730c120c952bf656d34687de5b8ec0","tid":558062,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f640a5779a4cb322b37ebbd858364453e59f81b9","tid":558062,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"等車個批最無辜"}]}